	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f104154497758976><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=135&mid=104154497758976>RE: Matches Dawnchaser</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=135&mid=104154497758976#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=74761><span id= >Balnore</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>97 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Jan 2nd 5:29 PM 2003</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.96]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>1hb useless? NO WAY<br><br>My weapons are as follows (from memory):<br><br>Troubador's Mace - 1hb<br>Di'Zok Wristsnapper - 1hb (range for stats)<br>Sion. Partisan - Pierce<br>Symphonic Saber - 1hs<br>Jagged Blade of Mourning - 1hs<br><br>Out of these, my best damage per second output comes from the Troub in primary and Partisan in secondary due mainly to the ratios.&nbsp;&nbsp;That being said, I just got the Jagged Blade so I have been experimenting with it in secondary and primary.  I have found that I do better with the Troub in primary.  For secondary I normally switch out for stats, ie, Jagged for Dex, Partisan for cha and int and Symphonic Saber for the stats and proc. (When I am crowd control, the cha and int help and the proc. once mez breaks, can, with one play of Katta dex song, move me from the top of the hate list to the bottom).<br><br>All that said, pre-epic, you can't beat the Troubador's Mace for the ratio, stats and brass instrument effect which rocks with several awesome buffs or AOE songs.  And if I get a superior range item, the Wristsnapper is going in my primary for the 10/18 ratio.<br><br>Long post to say that for bards, 1hb is not useless. Most epic holders I see have a 1hb in their other hand.<br><br>Sinfonian of the 52nd song<br>&nbsp;<br>Davidon<br>Wood Elf Druid<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=547810" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=547810</a><br><br>Sinfonian<br>Half-Elf Bard<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=547835" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=547835</a></td></tr>
